f_k(x)=\sum_{n=k}^\infty \left\{n\atop k\right\}x^n.
=\left\{k\atop k\right\}x^k+\sum_{n=k}^\infty\left\{n+1\atop k\right\} x^{n+1}
=x^k+x\sum_{n=k}^\infty\left(k\left\{n\atop k\right\}+\left\{n\atop k-1\right\}\right)x^n
